        "summary_cn": "本文提出ACE-ProtoNet，一种用于冠状动脉分割的自适应协方差特征门与不确定性感知原型学习网络。通过协方差特征门自适应筛选判别特征，并引入不确定性学习模块增强原型代表性。在心血管CT数据集上验证，该方法在分割精度与泛化能力上优于现有方法，为AI辅助医学图像分析提供新思路。",
        "abstract_excerpt": "“We propose ACE-ProtoNet, a novel network integrating adaptive covariance eigen-gate and uncertainty-aware prototype learning for coronary artery segmentation. The adaptive covariance eigen-gate selectively enhances discriminative features, while the uncertainty-aware module refines prototype representation by modeling feature ambiguity. Extensive experiments on coronary CT angiography datasets demonstrate that our method achieves superior segmentation accuracy and generalization compared to state-of-the-art approaches.”",
